<a href="https://www.youtube.com/" target="_blank">Link to YouTube</a> <!-- Called 'anchor', meaning it can link to another website with a hot link-->
<!-- the syntax above is call HTML attribute, modifies how an element behaves-->
<!-- Separate attributes with a space-->
<!-- The target attributes decides whether to open the link in the current tab or new tab-->

